  "link": "http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p718120/", 
  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p718120/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(128,0,128); line-height: 1.8em;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i1.s.hjfile.cn/entry/201406/c4eb420a-edc1-4d02-9c43-969dc82f4ef1.jpg\" /></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(128,0,128); line-height: 1.8em;\"><strong><a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/131781224/c2566/\" target=\"_blank\">《英闻天天译》</a></strong></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">是一档沪江部落的原创翻译互动节目（</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128,0,128); line-height: 1.8em;\"><a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/162087351441/\"><strong>戳去参与节目&gt;&gt;&gt;</strong></a></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">），主持人提供翻译参考文本，对大家递交的翻译作品进行点评，和大家共同进步！本期节目选</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">取的是关于</span>经济影响文学<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">的</span><span style=\"font-family: verdana, helvetica; line-height: 28px;\">一则英文报道，让我们一起在翻译中关注</span><font style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">。</font></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\"><span style=\"border-top: 0px;\"><span style=\"border-left-width: 0px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-image: none;\"><a><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i3.s.yun.hjfile.cn/entry/201501/fcfdeee9-09ca-4901-acaa-f899120481e7.jpeg!topic\" style=\"border-top: 0px; height: 342px; border-right: 0px; width: 500px; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px;\" /></a></span></span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\"><span style=\"border-top: 0px;\"><span style=\"border-left-width: 0px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-image: none;\"><strong>SUMMARY：</strong></span></span></span></p>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-variant: normal; white-space: normal; float: none; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-style: normal; line-height: 28px;\">2003年，约翰尼&middot;德普在电影《加勒比海盗：黑珍珠号的诅咒》中以另类的表演风格获得了第76届奥斯卡金像奖最佳男主角的提名。之后他又出演了这部电影的续集，德普那奇异的扮相和演技受到影迷的追捧。本文以另一种视角展现《加勒比海盗》是如何成就了德普，又如何毁灭了他？</span></span></div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">CONTENT：</strong></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tFor all his devoted fans, Depp had never been a true A-lister <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/command\" target=\"_blank\">command</a>ing tens of millions per picture &mdash; not with his <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/offbeat\" target=\"_blank\">offbeat</a> choices. But that all changed in 2003 when he signed onto his first big <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/blockbuster\" target=\"_blank\">blockbuster</a>. The movie was &ldquo;Pirates of the Caribbean: The Curse of the Black Pearl,&rdquo; based on a Disney ride, and Depp played Captain Jack Sparrow. He justified taking the part in various ways, &mdash; it was a movie his kids could see, it was a challenge to inject so much weirdness into a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/lightweight\" target=\"_blank\">lightweight</a> role. He brilliantly channeled Keith Richards for the role &mdash; <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/shamble\" target=\"_blank\">shambling</a> and <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/slur\" target=\"_blank\">slur</a>ring with a Cockney accent &mdash; though the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/eyeliner\" target=\"_blank\">eyeliner</a>, <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/dreadlock\" target=\"_blank\">dreadlock</a>s and goatee beards were all Depp&rsquo;s ideas (much to the chagrin of terrified Disney execs). The movie was a huge hit with moviegoers and also, surprisingly, the Academy. The role got him his first Oscar nomination.</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0,100,0);\"><strong>【沪江英语小编】</strong></span>大家在查看主持人提供的翻译版本前，可以先自己进行尝试翻译练习，只有在不断的翻译中翻译能力才能有所提升哦！<br />\n\t轻松注册沪江，马上参与<strong><a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/131781224/c2566/\">【英闻天天译】</a></strong>节目练翻译&rarr;<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/131781224/c2566/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/810ca373cf4442a188b39dd8ff64425f.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>本期节目参考译文：</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(128,128,128);\">（参考译文由该节目主持人提供，仅供参考，欢迎大家讨论）</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\"><strong>参考译文1：</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"replyview red\">\n\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\">对于德普的粉丝而言，他从来都不是凭借其另类的选择，拍一部戏可以赚取数以千万元的一线明星。但是当他2003年签约拍摄其第一部流行大片时，这一切都改变了。大片的名字是《加勒比海盗：黑珍珠号的诅咒》，根据迪士尼主题公园的同名景点制作，德普扮演船长杰克&middot;斯派洛。他证明了用多种方式扮演角色是可行的&mdash;&mdash;这是一部他的孩子可以观看的电影，也是将如此多的荒诞注入一个无足轻重的角色的挑战。他成功地说服了凯斯&middot;理查德兹扮演了一个走路蹒跚，说话含糊不清并带有考克尼口音的角色&mdash;&mdash;尽管眼线，长发绺和山羊胡都是德普的想法（这使受惊的迪士尼经理十分沮丧）。电影在影迷间十分受欢迎，并且令人惊喜的是，这在奥斯卡也造成了极大的轰动。德普凭借其角色第一次获得了奥斯卡提名。</span></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t想要得到主持人专业的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/162087351441/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255,0,0);\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</span></a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p718120/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p718120\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p715575/\">来跳坑！未来最受欢迎的十大职业</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p713491/\">看比尔盖茨如何写2014年终总结</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p451193/\">英国警察蜀黍爱卖萌：冒充警犬写个证词</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p720581/\">沪江小编教你如何避免春节尴尬瞬间</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p720009/\">英国装腔指南 像上流社会一样说英语</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p679466/\">囧研究 男人不论多大都喜欢22岁以下女人</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p717826/\">巧妙说不 4大招治好\"烂好人\"症</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p720792/\">山羊or绵羊？哭晕的“歪果仁”终于明白了！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p710833/\">等不及羊年：小羊率先穿圣诞毛衣街头闲逛</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0