  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/131781224/c2561/order2/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tLiquid<br />\n\tLiquid is the phase between solid and gas; it has a fix volume and takes on the shape of its container. What is the liquid? Where did it come from? How is it used?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: The <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/viscosity\" target=\"_blank\">viscosity</a> of the liquid is high... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/milkshake\" target=\"_blank\">milkshake</a> with various flavors<br />\n\t2) <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/lava\" target=\"_blank\">lava</a> flowing from the volcano<br />\n\t3) a melting ice cube<br />\n\t4) sweating runners in a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/marathon\" target=\"_blank\">marathon</a><br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWithout taking his eyes off this mysterious page, he put down his cup and reached over to his bag to get a pencil to jot down notes on the margin. That was when disaster struck &ndash; the strawberry latte was knocked over. Sean quickly grabbed the cup to stand it <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/upright\" target=\"_blank\">upright</a>, but it was still too late. Although he had drunk most of the latte, what remained was now spreading on the table. He jumped up. One of his hands picked up his bag, and the other took the papers off the table. The pink liquid was now nearing the edge of the table.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/161661537811/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p718973/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p718973\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p715575/\">来跳坑！未来最受欢迎的十大职业</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p713491/\">看比尔盖茨如何写2014年终总结</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p451193/\">英国警察蜀黍爱卖萌：冒充警犬写个证词</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p720581/\">沪江小编教你如何避免春节尴尬瞬间</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p720009/\">英国装腔指南 像上流社会一样说英语</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p679466/\">囧研究 男人不论多大都喜欢22岁以下女人</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p717826/\">巧妙说不 4大招治好\"烂好人\"症</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p720792/\">山羊or绵羊？哭晕的“歪果仁”终于明白了！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p710833/\">等不及羊年：小羊率先穿圣诞毛衣街头闲逛</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http:/