now.</p>\n<p>\n\tWendy：There's a place in heaven where we'll go.</p>\n<p>\n\t小慧：If heaven is a millions away.</p>\n<p>\n\tOh just call me and I make your day.</p>\n<p>\n\t小媛：When the nights are getting cold and blue.</p>\n<p>\n\t饼干 ：When the days are getting hard for you.</p>\n<p>\n\t饼干：I will always stay here by your side.</p>\n<p>\n\t小媛：I promise you I'll never hide.</p>\n<p>\n\t全体合唱：But if you wanna cry.</p>\n<p>\n\tCry on my shoulder.</p>\n<p>\n\tIf you need someone who cares for you.</p>\n<p>\n\tIf you're feeling sad your heart gets colder.</p>\n<p>\n\t小媛 ：Yes I show you what real love can do.</p>\n<p>\n\t饼干：But if you wanna cry.</p>\n<p>\n\tCry on my shoulder.</p>\n<p>\n\tWendy 小媛 小慧：If you need someone</p>\n<p>\n\t饼干：who cares for you.</p>\n<p>\n\twendy：if you're feeling sad your heart gets colder.</p>\n<p>\n\tYes I show you what real love can do.</p>\n<p>\n\tWhat real love can do.</p>\n<p>\n\tWhat real love can do.</p>\n<p>\n\tWhat love can do.</p>\n<p>\n\tWhat love can do.</p>\n<p>\n\t❀ 没有迈不过的槛，人定胜天，我们相信，在全国人民的一起努力下，四川雅安的人民一定能克服困难，你们的将来一定会更好！</p>\n<p>\n\t❀ 加油雅安，平安，这一刻我们都是雅安人！为你们祈福！</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">讲解：<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p720258\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">想要得到主持人专业的点评和意见吗？</span><a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15093/item/927691/\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p720258/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p720258\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p715575/\">来跳坑！未来最受欢迎的十大职业</